	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. P.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod tam raro ad pietatem tuam scribo, in causa est penuria novarum te dignarum, et nugis nolo illi esse molestus.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quę pauca autem ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName> habemus, omnia m. d. <persName type="citizen_name">Fabritio</persName> exposui, ut eadem pietati tuę comunicet, rogavique, ut salutationes meas addat, quod iddem his addo et obsequiorum meorum perpetuam pietati tuę obtulionem.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Datum <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curię Rhetorum</placeName> 22. novembris 1558.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">P[ietatis] t[uae] obsequentissimus amicus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8306" cert="high">J. Ja. Decambray</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro pietate et eruditione excellenti domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, Tigurinę ecclesiae ministro, domino et amico suo colendo.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Adresse wahrscheinlich von anderer Hand]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
